Summary: Pyscanlogd is a port scan detection tool written in Python
Home-page: http://code.google.com/p/pyscanlogd
Author: pythonhacker
Author-email: python.thehacker@gmail.com
License: GPL
Description: Pyscanlogd is a port scan detection tool written in pure Python. It can
        detect most fast port scans and even can detect port-scans of longer
        duration upto an hour. It can run as a daemon as well as in the foreground.
        
